Command> glab mr update $1

Argument> $1: id, branch

Keywords> gitlab
        > mr

Example01> glab mr update 23 --ready
Example02> glab mr update 23 --draft
Example03> glab mr update --draft  # Updates MR related to current branch

Reference> https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/blob/main/docs/source/mr/update.md
